{"tid":2189357,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–改變ABO血型","createTime":"2020-09-04T23:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T21:31:54.000Z","uid":38861,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"74ef4df2946aa3ec31a50e13b62babe7aaa82ef6","tid":2189357,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T23:07:37.000Z","msg":"血型有很多種分類方法，較為最用的是ABO血型及Rh+-方法，原因是這兩種方法尤其是ABO血型方面出現不配合情況的話，將會引起實際上的醫學負面效果。<br />\n<br />\n而其他類型血型分辨方式得出的結果就算有所不吻合，也不會釀成重大或可見的醫學問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/me70eQr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fme70eQr.jpg&h=890cba9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖1）ABO血型的界定，取決於紅血球上的表面糖份組織結構，而每個紅血球的表面則接近有差唔多一百萬份這些糖份組織結構。<br />\n<br />\n除紅血球外，身體器官各細胞也擁有這些ABO糖份組織，所以在器官移植領域上亦相當重視ABO的吻合度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oN96aoP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoN96aoP.jpg&h=691a4d2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）我們體內產生的抗體，將會用來對抗外來品種的紅血球。<br />\n<br />\nO型血的人體內會產生出對抗A及B型糖份結構的抗體，摧毀對應的紅血球功能，因此沒法接收A、B或者AB血型的血液。<br />\n<br />\n有一點值得注意的是，無論任何血型的血液也好，我們體內均沒有對抗O血型糖份結構的抗體。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qw4FeRL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqw4FeRL.jpg&h=d9d33386&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）正因為沒有O型抗體這回事，若然利用蛋白酶改變紅血球表面的糖份組織結構，就能夠統一將所有血型O型化，簡化思考抗體排斥的問題。<br />\n<br />\n這是不少科學家一直在研究的問題，事實上早在80年代已成功把B型血轉化成為O型血，但所需的功夫並不符合成本效益。<br />\n<br />\n現時科學家們已逐步找出合適及有效率的蛋白酶能夠轉化各血型為O血型（Ref1)，若能夠在學界及醫學界裡取得共識的話，將會在器官移植方面尤其有用，大幅度減免各種不理想的排斥反應。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"red\">like</span>以及<span class=\"green\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs4%2BrkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=9946dfcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs4%2BrkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=dd429eb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1: <a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6956546/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC6956546%2F&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs4%2BrkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=8b965b69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6956546/</a>"},{"pid":"ad02da9f0d0bb64e0d3b5900911f45c47e250fa3","tid":2189357,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T23:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac225e3d050d061e7f1ea16aaad15197266f3d99","tid":2189357,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T23:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb8c85ca10b1e3e4006b5e77a657689456c8530c","tid":2189357,"uid":341842,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T00:00:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces